## 7. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Notes |
|-------|-----------|-------|
| EHR server | HAPI FHIR R4 (Docker) | `hapiproject/hapi:latest` |
| Synthetic data | Synthea | v3.x, FHIR R4 output mode |
| Agent framework | Raw Claude tool-use API | Direct tool_use/tool_result loop, no framework |
| LLM (dev) | `claude-haiku-4-5` | Fast and cheap during development |
| LLM (prod) | `claude-sonnet-4-5` | Used for final demo and letter generation |
| PDF extraction | `pdfplumber` | Pure Python, no external calls |
| Speech-to-text | `faster-whisper` | Runs fully local, `base.en` model |
| Risk model | CatBoost binary classifier | Trained fresh on MIMIC-IV or CMS DE-SynPUF |
| ICD-10 lookup | Local JSON dataset | CMS 2025 ICD-10-CM flat file |
| Backend | FastAPI + uvicorn | SSE via `sse-starlette` |
| Frontend | React + Vite | Plain fetch, no heavy UI library |
| Containerization | Docker Compose | HAPI + backend as services |

