## 11. Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|------------|
| Claude tool-use loop takes longer than expected | Low | Skeleton is ~200 lines; Anthropic docs have clear examples |
| `faster-whisper` slow on CPU | Low | Use `base.en` model; batch audio offline |
| MIMIC-IV access delayed beyond 2 days | Medium | Fall back to CMS DE-SynPUF immediately — apply for both on Day 1 |
| CatBoost training slow on large dataset | Low | Start with `iterations=500`; subsample to 100k rows if needed — AUC impact is minimal |
| Denial label engineering produces imbalanced classes | Medium | Use `scale_pos_weight` or `class_weights` in CatBoost; log class distribution in training README |
| Claude letter quality inconsistent | Low | Few-shot prompt with example letter; temperature 0.3 |
| Epic sandbox not approved in time | High | HAPI FHIR is the primary data layer; Epic is upside |

